divs: Sighting DetailsThis was caught on camera and was found later that evening when reviewing the photos. The object is located to the right of the falling booster rockets. In my opinion looks like a bat, at my best explanation. Please let me know what you may think of it. I only added our photography name to the photo. If you would request an unedited photo, please let me know. The photo was taken of the booster rocket separation during the shuttle launch.
